<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>When $config is not set, throwing the exception :</p>

<p>{{throw new Zend_Config_Exception("Cannot find $config array in $filename");}}</p>

<p>triggers a PHP notice:</p>

<p>{{Undefined variable: config in path-to-ZF-library/Zend/Config/Array.php on line 58}}</p>

<p>my fix is to replace the double quotes with simple quotes:</p>

<p>{{throw new Zend_Config_Exception('Cannot find $config array in $filename');}}</p>

    </div>
